# Content Collection Best Practices

This document outlines the standards and best practices for managing content collections in the portfolio site.

## Collection Types

### Content Collections (`type: "content"`)
Use for Markdown or MDX content that requires frontmatter:
- Articles
- Case Studies
- Documentation

### Data Collections (`type: "data"`)
Use for structured data in JSON format:
- Services
- Site Content
- Configuration

## Directory Structure

```
src/content/
├── config.ts           # Collection configuration
├── articles/          # Markdown content
│   └── *.md
├── case-studies/      # Markdown content
│   └── *.md
├── services/         # JSON data
